This directory contains the user-facing HTML manuals for the Regalia app
(Chinese and English versions). Each manual is a self-contained HTML file
with embedded CSS and JavaScript (no external resources).

License classification by file:
  - Regalia-v1.0.6-manual-zh.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      Chinese user manual for Regalia v1.0.6.
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - Regalia-v1.0.6-manual-en.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      English user manual for Regalia v1.0.6.
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - Regalia-v1.0.5-manual-zh.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      Chinese user manual for Regalia v1.0.5 (kept for historical reference).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - Regalia-v1.0.5-manual-en.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      English user manual for Regalia v1.0.5 (kept for historical reference).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - Regalia-v1.0.4-manual-zh.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      Chinese user manual for Regalia v1.0.4 (kept for historical reference).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
  - Regalia-v1.0.4-manual-en.html: AGPL v3 (original Regalia work)
      English user manual for Regalia v1.0.4 (kept for historical reference).
      Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.

The manuals are AGPL v3 because they are original documentation created by
the Regalia project, not derived from any third-party GPL work. The embedded
diagrams, wireframes, and changelog text are all original.

v1.0.6 (2026.6.27) changes:
  - Regalia-v1.0.6-manual-zh.html: New v1.0.6 manual with all v1.0.6
    changelog entries (Chess960 ECO suppression, PGN FEN round-trip
    preservation, stats.html per-move selection, unified gray-out styling,
    portrait-optimized new game settings, scroll-position preservation,
    engine-eval FEN sanitization, king-then-rook castling gesture,
    Chess960 castling detection fix, SL mode skill-level display).
  - Regalia-v1.0.6-manual-en.html: Synced with Chinese version.
  - Regalia-v1.0.5 and v1.0.4 manuals: kept for historical reference only.

v1.0.5 Round-6 Rev54 changes:
  - Regalia-v1.0.5-manual-zh.html: Updated with Rev54 changelog entry
    (yellow/blue arrow extensions, per-color arrow offsets, yellow
    rounded-rect square style, roll-only board rotation, first-principles
    anti-shake audit with GAME_ROTATION_VECTOR preference).
  - Regalia-v1.0.5-manual-en.html: Synced with Chinese version.
  - No changes to v1.0.4 manuals (historical reference only).

